{"lemma":"مَلِكَةُ","slug":"مَلِكَةُ","root":"م.ل.ك","root_slug":"م-ل-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/م-ل-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n43691","n43692","n43705"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%90%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"queen"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"possession"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"acquisition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"attainment, acquired skill or quality, talent, virtue","examples":[{"text":"وَٱلْمَلَكَاتُ لَا تَحْصُلُ إلَّا بِتَكْرَارِ الْأَفْعَالِ، لِأَنَّ الْفِعْلَ يَقَعُ أَوَّلًا، وَتَعُودُ مِنْهُ لِلذَّاتِ صِفَةٌ، ثُمَّ تَتَكَرَّرُ فَتَكُونُ حَالًا. وَمَعْنَى الْحَالِ أَنَّهَا صِفَةٌ غَيْرُ رَاسِخَةٍ ثُمَّ يَزِيدُ التَّكْرَارُ فَتَكُونُ مَلَكَةً أَيْ صِفَةً رَاسِخَةً."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"habit, custom"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"slavery"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ma.li.ka/","/ma.la.ka/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n43691","headword_ar":"مَلَكَهُ","root":"mlk","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He possessed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"owned it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with ability to have it to himself exclusively:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he exercised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had, authority over it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mulokN","text_ar":"مُلْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exercise of authority to command and to forbid in respect of the generality of a people"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]: (Er-Rághib, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having possession and command"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"authority:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having power to exercise command"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"authority."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"milokN","text_ar":"مِلْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malakahu","text_ar":"مَلَكَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He possessed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is more common than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malokN","text_ar":"مَلْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mulokN","text_ar":"مُلْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaka A^amorahu","text_ar":"مَلَكَ اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had the ruling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordering, of his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaka EalaY Aln~aAsi A^amorahumo","text_ar":"مَلَكَ عَلَى النَّاسِ اَمْرَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had the dominion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sovereignty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ruling power, over the people."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-  See 4."}],"source_refs":["M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n43692","headword_ar":"مَلَّكَهُ","root":"mlk","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to possess"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; (S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amolakahu","text_ar":"اَمْلَكَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him king;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made him to have dominion, kingship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rule."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yumal~aka Alr~ajulu A^amorahu","text_ar":"يُمَلَّكَ الرَّجُلُ اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The man shall be made to have the ruling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordering, of his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Sh, T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dyn","text_ar":"دين"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n43705","headword_ar":"مَلَكَةٌ","root":"mlk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A faculty."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quality firmly rooted in the mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KT.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}